latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Building the Cat Trial 12: No Hands obstacle course in the desert came with its challenges. See how it all came together in this time lapse video.

See more at Cat.com/Trial12

Just like soccer players, our autonomous machines are nimble and precise. See how in Cat Trial 12: No Hands. #CatTrials 

Learn more at Cat.com/CatTrials

Kids say the darndest things, right?  #BringYourChildToWorkDay is this week so we asked #TeamCaterpillar to ask their favorite little ones what they think we do at work. Check out what they had to say. #iAmCaterpillar
See how FIRST Robotics helps students develop the skills we need to help customers build a better tomorrow.

During Cat Trial 10: Tech Test, technicians showed off their talents with fun, job-related challenges. In the latest edition of Concept to Reality, we found these tasks are a lot tougher than they look.

Dealer technicians help keep our customers up and running. The demand for technicians is greater than ever and Cat dealers are hiring thousands every year to keep up with customer needs. Find out how to get started: www.caterpillar.com/dealertech

We put MotoGP star @jackmilleraus to the test against our Global Operator Challenge runner up (and European champ) Tommy Murphy. Watch them operate a 302.7 mini excavator to see who's the fastest Cat driver.

We're celebrating 50 years of Caterpillar Demonstration & Learning Centers. The three centers are where our customers get to experience Cat products and services first-hand — either in person or through our virtual programs. 

Watch to hear more on our facilities @caterpillaredwards, @caterpillartinajahills and @caterpillarmalaga. And visit cat.com/operatortraining for their training services.

Knowing how to troubleshoot problems and find the best solution is what being a service tech is all about.

Watch our tech contestants put their troubleshooting skills to the test in Webisode 8. See more at caterpillar.com/dealertech.

Most days you’ll find our engineers using 3D printers to create parts and assemblies. But every so often, they use them to help save lives.

Watch to see how we used the latest 3D printing technology to support doctors at @osfhealth.

As the heavy equipment provider for @pbr we help get arenas across the U.S. ready for the action. See what it takes in our latest Concept to Reality.

#LetsDoTheWork
